{"tid":317864,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"重睇獵人一問","createTime":"2017-07-11T17:32:49.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-12T05:48:05.000Z","uid":33684,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"ebf6ea6871806da90f47752f46ece4d1b4d8a09e","tid":317864,"uid":33684,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-11T17:32:49.000Z","msg":"西裝眼鏡入蟻王宮殿佈置出口果時畀念嚇親<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/12/012704_129165b0386ffaf8fec8b519660cbcb6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F12%2F012704_129165b0386ffaf8fec8b519660cbcb6.jpg&h=e1f494b8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n跟住仲有少少係講佢走去偷睇佢個學生貞子被車車入去<br />\n但唔關事我唔貼啦<br />\n<br />\n我想問既係點解最後佢會行出宮殿<br />\n而唔係偷睇完貞子就直接係地下畫圈圈出黎呢？<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/12/012504_d5fa2fd7bb3a2facd8c1288175213106.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F12%2F012504_d5fa2fd7bb3a2facd8c1288175213106.jpg&h=c149dcef&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n如果佢畫圈圈走既話 係咪可以直接傳送係更遠既地方？<br />\n定係我理解錯左佢既能力"},{"pid":"c23249b504e1e1e6c81c2de972408edfb9c2944e","tid":317864,"uid":61832,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-11T17:39:53.000Z","msg":"劇情需要"},{"pid":"cfd3dc75b6a3251becbc9da526fb3df44d97f96d","tid":317864,"uid":33684,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-11T17:56:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>劇情需要</blockquote><br />\n其實佢傳送出黎都唔影響劇情<br />\n不過有傳送門都要行出黎好似有d反智<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"844656254fe73d8f5a4f128763fbcdfd600ef043","tid":317864,"uid":29613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-11T18:23:44.000Z","msg":"個陣唔係話佢淨係可以入去畫圏但唔可以發動能力？<br />\n因為一用就比人發現<br />\n佢要用絕入去做野，所以要跑番出黎<br />\n<br />\n靠記憶，錯左唔好屌"},{"pid":"8a6b39019e0527369bfba391c67a8f57dda540f2","tid":317864,"uid":100474,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-11T18:30:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>個陣唔係話佢淨係可以入去畫圏但唔可以發動能力？<br />\n因為一用就比人發現<br />\n佢要用絕入去做野，所以要跑番出黎<br />\n<br />\n靠記憶，錯左唔好屌</blockquote><br />\n唔係掛 佢唔係郁手殺左隻發現佢嘅蟻咩<br />\n我睇漫畫覺得係佢出左最遠嘅門<br />\n再往外跑"},{"pid":"13d9aab3c9495c438e8027ace9644bfb747fc1aa","tid":317864,"uid":33684,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-11T19:31:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>個陣唔係話佢淨係可以入去畫圏但唔可以發動能力？<br />\n因為一用就比人發現<br />\n佢要用絕入去做野，所以要跑番出黎<br />\n<br />\n靠記憶，錯左唔好屌</blockquote><br />\n唔係掛 佢唔係郁手殺左隻發現佢嘅蟻咩<br />\n我睇漫畫覺得係佢出左最遠嘅門<br />\n再往外跑</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n睇返開post貼果張圖 四眼當時跑出黎個位置同下面呢張潛入果時既位置差唔多<br />\n<img src=\"http://pic2.sfacg.com/Pic/OnlineComic1/HunterXHunter/250/006_28324.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fpic2.sfacg.com%2FPic%2FOnlineComic1%2FHunterXHunter%2F250%2F006_28324.jpg&h=42ad62a4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n呢張圖係250話<br />\n但一來唔見佢有出到傳送門 我睇動畫版都無<br />\n二來呢個應該唔係最遠既門<br />\n因為佢同煙剷有係城市作戰過 之後再去潛入<br />\n咁佢其實最起碼都可以傳送去個城到"},{"pid":"d2549856857a76e6926f8d2e1f0fda7fd04d8f9d","tid":317864,"uid":33684,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T05:42:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3b2752f0576fdd2c80779f5b983d74cf09555a44","tid":317864,"uid":109185,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T05:44:09.000Z","msg":"依家上船個到好似有啲唔知做緊咩咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"06c0a5c3268cde5a5cf0f236e808ebc62c2c40c7","tid":317864,"uid":111253,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T05:48:05.000Z","msg":"Set好門，俾念嚇親，俾你仲敢唔敢開多次技？一旦被發現能力，成班蟻用隨意門殺你全家，緊係用絕行返轉頭"}]}